name: EQUILIBRIO 2017
description: This is a national level techno cultural fest of central university (IT-GGV). It's going to be future's largest technological festival of central india.

name: Sabrang 2017
description: SABRANG is Annual Tech-Management fest of JK Lakshmipat University. Its a 2 day event full of exciting Competition in regards of Management and Technology. Get ready to explore the colors of psyche and celebration in this vibrant gathering of young enthusiasm . We at JK Lakshmipat University invite you to Sabrang, to join us in these two days of extravaganza where we celebrate,commemorate and culminate your passion.

name: Kashiyatra IIT BHU Varanasi
description: Indian Institute of Technology (Banaras Hindu University) Varanasi presents its annual socio-cultural festival, Kashiyatra. Kashiyatra or KY, is a 3-day long extravaganza blending the disciplines of music, literature and arts into a fest of gargantuan proportions. Over the years, Kashiyatra has grown to become one of the biggest galas of North India with a footfall of 25,000+ college students spanning the entire nation. This edition, we bring you a Millennial Reprise to take you on a nostalgic ride to the unforgettable 90's.

name: ZEAL 2017
description: We take immense pleasure and honour in presenting to you the annual management festival of IBS Pune, Zeal 2017, which is scheduled to take place on 13th and 14th January, 2017. Zeal 2017 will showcase the intellectual and creative talent that IBS Pune possesses, giving each participant an opportunity to experience, learn and execute, with no reins attached.

name: Chrysalis 2017
description: It's the second edition of the hottest literary fest in town conducted by English department of Bharata Mata college, Kochi. Back with the theme ' Illumine life, give them wings' and lot of surprises and its all for a cause.

name: Saarang 2017
description: Get set to witness India's largest student-run fest in this country. Wherever you are, 'apparate' and reach IIT Madras to see the forest come alive. The enchantment shall be open to viewing from 4th January, 2017 to 8th January, 2017. Register on our website now.
contact: publicrelations@saarang.org Please check the website for the contact details for the cores of the different departments at Saarang.

name: CONVERGE 2017
description: Converge is the annual techno-cultural-managerial festivals of Jaypee Institute of Information Technology, Noida, Sector-128 (JIIT, Noida). It was founded by Jaiprakash Sewa Sansthan. This pulsating festival with an array of events, allowing the students a chance to exhibit and participate in technical and academic pursuits of programming, robotics, B-plan competitions, panel discussions, talk shows and many more such creative challenges. It also provides ample opportunities to the young students of today to experience and live their passion doing theme walks, fashions shows, sports and at the same time express their talent and versatility through choreography and street plays.

name: Advaita 17
description: IIIT Bhubaneswar presents its 5th edition of Inter-college Techno-Cult festival, ADVAITA'17 from 9th feb'17 to 12th feb'17. We would like you to be a part of this Extravaganza.

name: Echoes 17
description: Indian Institute of Management, Kozhikode better known as God's Own Campus is proud to present its national level cultural festival Echoes'17 which will be held from February 3-5,2017. ECHOES 2016 featured a wide variety of competitions in the fields of Music, Dance, Fashion, Art and Theatre with participation from colleges across India and prizes worth over INR 3.5 lakhs. Over the years ECHOES has become a name synonymous with the biggest pro-nites in South India with live performances by Raghu Dixit Project, Shilpa rao, Aditi Singh Sharma, Nikhil D'Souza, Neeraj Sridhar, Suraj Jagan, Anushka Manchanda, Thermal and a Quarter, Junkyard Groove, Sona Mohapatra, Agnee and many more. The theme for Echoes 2017 is Good Old 90's; and this year promises to be novel not only in the theme but also in the stunning array of new events we have added to make the experience more memorable.

name: NrTHYA 2K17
description: Nrthya 2k17 Is the First Ever all Kerala inter-college Dance Fest Conducted by Bharata Mata College,thrikkakara.it Is an initiative to invite Young and Talented Youth to Put their best Foot forward

name: VIBE 2k17
description: One good thing about music- When it hits you, you will feel no pain.

name: Enquizta 2017
description: Enquizta is the quizzing event of Kashiyatra.

name: SYNERGY 17
description: Synergy 2017 is an International Technical Symposium organized by Institution of Electronics and Telecommunication Engineers Student Forum(ISF) in association with School of Electronics and Telecommunication Engineering - VIT University, Vellore. Synergy'17 looks forward to promote 'Rekindle Innovation', which not only embraces one's desire to become better, but also enables one to be able to explain the myriad of emotions a person experiences on the path to success and spread the word. Our goal is to create a stage where amazing talents can be brought to light, some maybe even hidden deep within those who never really got a chance to explore themselves. We are stepping up to provide an opportunity; to create your own conundrums, enable you with the most optimal solutions and manifest the endowment of young budding and brisk minds.

name: MIND OVER MATTER 2K17
description: We are proud to announce that our institute is coming up with the 3rd edition of Mind Over Matter -2K17, after unprecedented success of its previous two editions. Continuing with IIITM's tradition of being a pioneer in the field of Innovation, this year MOM will take things up by a notch.

name: SYNOPIA 2017
description: Leash the anger on purpose. Unleash it when falling apart. Playing the game of leashing and unleashing, while using your mind to stand within yet stand apart brings out the true essence of Synopia. Bringing out the manager in you, being at the edge of your creativity, gaming your heart out, from being a photographer to playing street sport with spontaneity is what you need to be a part of this extravaganza, fun filled event that has been growing more and more glorious with each year.

name: Top International Educational Faculty and Students Awards 2017
description: TOP INTERNATIONAL EDUCATIONAL FACULTY AND STUDENTS AWARDS-2017

description: An event that will make you wanna paricipate
